OL,3,CRaye's campaign for songwriters wins
OL,4,Cspecial award
OL,6,FRaye, 27, whose real name is Rachel
OL,7,FAgatha Keen, will receive the honour
OL,8,Fat a ceremony in central London in
OL,9,FOctober for "using her platform to
OL,10,Fdemand greater transparency and fairer
OL,11,Fpay between labels and artists".
OL,13,FThe seven-time Brit Award winner,
OL,14,Fknown for her hit songs Prada and
OL,15,FEscapism, has been described by the
OL,16,Facademy as "one of the most outspoken
OL,17,Fand influential advocates for
OL,18,Fsongwriters, using her platform to
OL,19,Finspire fellow musicians and bring
OL,20,Fabout positive change".
