OL,3,CRaye's campaign for songwriters wins
OL,4,Cspecial award
OL,6,FThis comes after the singer called out
OL,7,Flabel executives at the Ivors 2024
OL,8,Fceremony, urging the music industry to
OL,9,Freward the "voiceless beating heart of
OL,10,Fthe industry, which is songwriters".
OL,12,FRoberto Neri, chief executive of The
OL,13,FIvors Academy, said: "An incredible
OL,14,Fmulti-award-winning artist, RAYE is
OL,15,Fone of the most gifted songwriters of
OL,16,Fher generation and always gives full
OL,17,Frespect and voice to fellow writers.
