OL,3,CRaye's campaign for songwriters wins
OL,4,Cspecial award
OL,6,F"She has consistently called for
OL,7,Fbetter pay and greater recognition for
OL,8,Fsongwriters, championing structural
OL,9,Fchange to protect the talent behind
OL,10,Fthe music we love.
OL,12,F"We're proud to honour her with this
OL,13,Fwell-deserved recognition."
OL,15,FThe Ivors Academy Honour aims to
OL,16,Fcelebrate people who champion
OL,17,Fsongwriters and composers and help
OL,18,F"build a stronger, fairer and more
OL,19,Finclusive music industry."
