OL,3,CRaye's campaign for songwriters wins
OL,4,Cspecial award
OL,6,FDespite her talent, her solo work did
OL,7,Fnot reach the same heights, and in
OL,8,F2021, she expressed frustration at her
OL,9,Flabel not letting her release her
OL,10,Fdebut album yet.
OL,12,FBy the end of 2022, she had struck out
OL,13,Fon her own and her dance track
OL,14,FEscapism featuring 070 Shake went
OL,15,Fviral on TikTok, shooting up the
OL,16,Fcharts to number one.
OL,18,FShe later released her album My 21st
OL,19,FCentury Blues in 2023, which reached
OL,20,Fnumber two on the UK album charts
